summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4458 for the improvement of the alley in Block 10, York Addition, being the alley between 34th Avenue South and 35th Avenue South, from Hinds Street to Horton Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 52572, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
